{"tid":622313,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌奶星 卷二作文考人識唔識禁區","createTime":"2018-04-09T05:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T05:16:37.000Z","uid":60506,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d16f800476878ff4c1fd9c0ac9df7b4b2bcc934","tid":622313,"uid":60506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:13:10.000Z","msg":"2. 日常生活之中，有各種各樣的禁區。試就個人的想像或思考，以「禁區」為題，寫作文章一篇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我梗係諗都唔諗即刻第一時間寫晒球例啦，邊度為止禁區 龍門球邊個位開波 寫完已經差唔多700字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住又講下牙朗可以係禁區玩跳水 360度芭蕾舞旋轉，呢到又300幾字....<br />\n<br />\n去到埋尾就加少少講下上星期call完g既個人感想 講下班女點樣懶係要守護自己禁區，見到錢就乖乖做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢到輕輕鬆鬆都成1500字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今年考評局真係明益我地波台手足<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/titter.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Ftitter.gif&h=e942c2db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db25b963a9166c34b43ca034a1d2a2a466f06618","tid":622313,"uid":60506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"系"}]}